        The type of document created by the sample sheet importer when confronted with extract IDs for which no Geneious documents exist yet. Note that the corresponding Geneious type is the same as it is for FASTA, because V1 of the Naturalis plugin did create a DefaultNucleotideSequence document with some dummy default values (e.g. "NNNNNNNNNN" for the nucleotide sequence).
